                    <p style='margin-top:0in;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:115%;font-size:15px;font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif;text-align:right;'><span dir="RTL" style='font-size:16px;line-height:115%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;'>المسؤولية التي تحكم استخدام موقعنا الإلكتروني</span><span dir="RTL" style='font-size:16px;line-height:115%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;'>.</span><span dir="RTL" style='font-size:16px;line-height:115%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;'>&nbsp;</span><strong><span style='font-size:16px;line-height:115%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;'>ipersona.me</span></strong><span dir="RTL" style='font-size:16px;line-height:115%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;'>&nbsp;خلال زيارة الرابط الت</span><span dir="RTL" style='font-size:16px;line-height:115%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;'>الي&nbsp;</span><span dir="RTL" style='font-size:16px;line-height:115%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;'>.</span></p>
                    <p style='margin-top:0in;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:115%;font-size:15px;font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif;text-align:right;'><span dir="RTL" style='font-size:16px;line-height:115%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;'>&nbsp;</span></p>
